<P><FONT COLOR="#FF0000"><FONT SIZE=+2>骨幹網路(Backbone Network)</FONT></FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>
</FONT></P>

<UL>
<P><IMG SRC="../../gif/redcube.gif" HEIGHT=18 WIDTH=18><FONT SIZE=+1>將連結設備(bridge,
